description:
“When you pray,” Jesus tells us, “enter into your closet, and when you have shut your door, pray to your Father which is in secret…” Matthew 6:6. Why is God “in secret”? Why doesn’t He openly show Himself to the whole world? He will. SOON. Now is the time to prepare for the Big Day.
